		<h4>LEAGUE RULES......PLEASE READ THEM CAREFULLY !!</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>A person has an option to Join as many Leagues as he wants.</li>
				<li>A person can Create only ONE league, i.e.; he can own only ONE League.</li>
				<li>Once a person creates a League, the system will generate a secret code, the owner has to preserve that code so that this code can be shared with people who want to join that particular League.</li>
				<li>On Joining/Creating a particular League, the system will allocate 8100 points to every user for that League.</li>
				<li>On Joining/Creating a particular League, the system will allow the person to predict for all matches from 29th April to 24th May.</li>
				<li>Once points for a match are submitted, the system shall deduct the points from the League balance of the user.</li>
				<li>Prediction once saved, cannot be altered or changed.</li>
				<li>If a person does not predict or forgets to predict, then the system will deduct default value of 200 points for League matches, 500 points for Qualifier and Eliminator Matches and 1000 for Final Match.</li>
				<li>Put Minimum 200 Points for League Matches, 500 for Qualifier and Eliminator Matches and 1000 for Final Match, else the system will not allow you to submit.</li>
			</ul>
